    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit is equipped with a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. It maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and a linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains true, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback enthusiasts demand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
