    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A4 Premium Plus that perfectly strikes the balance between luxury performance and daily utility. The exterior, finished in a deep Moonlight Blue Metallic, retains a high-gloss shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical for a vehicle that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the Nougat Brown leather upholstery is in excellent shape, with no tears or heavy staining, and the genuine wood inlays remain vibrant. Every feature, from the Audi Virtual Cockpit to the heated steering wheel and Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts seamlessly. I have a complete service history, including a recent 40,000-mile major service and a fresh set of all-season tires installed last season. This car has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly. It is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for many more miles of comfortable commuting.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
