    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle offers a distinguished combination of performance and enduring value. Benefiting from a comprehensive service history and a rigorous multi-point inspection, it presents in commendable mechanical and aesthetic order. An ideal selection for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience, this unit stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains prepared for immediate service.",
      "price": 34800.0,
