    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a quality car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
