      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The powertrain is in excellent health, with a recently overhauled VANOS system ensuring precise variable valve timing and a linear power band. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. Equipped with the M Variable Differential Lock and individual throttle bodies, the car offers exceptional throttle mapping and mechanical grip. While the aesthetics show honest patina, the suspension bushings are firm and the steering rack remains communicative, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
